==English==
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#A [[slat]]ted opening in a wall, door or window.
#Any of a series of narrow openings framed at their longer edges with slanting, overlapping fins or slats, adjustablefor admitting light and air while shutting out rain.
#A fin or slat framing such an opening.
#A ventilating turret or lantern, as on the roof of a medieval building.
#Any of a system of slits, asin the hood of an automobile, for ventilation.

